title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Rapper Reese Laflare
description:
On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with Reese Laflare, we’re fucking around with the worst style in Atlanta, producers, getting reckless in the studio, celebrity crushes, weed carriers, shooters, merch interns, slang, designer vs. streetwear and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
